ry cards could result in black screen", "(backlight not set) when rebooting the panel.", "No support of mp3-format. #21639 The Dialogue will be presented but not be able to play the", "mp3-format in the built in Media player feature. Audio out", "is not supported on X2 panels", "PDF-viewer limitations. #21641 Bookmark limitations when using the built in PDF-viewer", "feature.", "Vertical scroll picker height too small to maneuver.", "DHCP (Dynamic IP setting) #22540 It is always recommended to use the Static IP settings.", "LAN A = default Static IP", "LAN B = default DHCP IP (Dynamic)", "The configuration for the LAN-ports can be configured via", "the Service menu, see manual for details.", "SD-card writing #22655 Repeat the write procedure if the SD-card write error", "appears.", "www.beijerelectronics.com 2016-10-03 PIEN345 Page 1 of 2"], "bbox": [[0.274172, 0.05761, 0.588497, 0.018954], [0.071558, 0.120873, 0.06797300000000002, 0.013111], [0.181449, 0.128854, 0.08629499999999998, 0.013111], [0.071558, 0.136977, 0.057291999999999996, 0.013111], [0.067527, 0.156073, 0.23511000000000004, 0.013111], [0.177417, 0.172177, 0.278457, 0.013111], [0.177417, 0.188281, 0.16950899999999997, 0.013111], [0.177417, 0.204385, 0.302268, 0.013111], [0.177417, 0.220488, 0.20387, 0.013111], [0.071558, 0.278653, 0.535242, 0.01936], [0.378435, 0.332395, 0.016044999999999976, 0.013111], [0.071558, 0.342228, 0.616756, 0.013111], [0.378435, 0.352062, 0.06995499999999999, 0.013111], [0.481439, 0.371933, -0.046437000000000006, 0.015733], [0.481439, 0.387609, -0.362869, 0.015733], [0.481439, 0.403285, 0.412854, 0.015733], [0.481439, 0.418961, 0.06307100000000004, 0.015733], [0.067527, 0.458945, 0.839891, 0.013111], [0.067527, 0.475049, 0.21384599999999998, 0.013111], [0.067527, 0.519821, 0.855655, 0.013111], [0.067527, 0.535925, 0.8187220000000001, 0.013111], [0.481439, 0.552028, 0.340786, 0.013111], [0.067527, 0.57711, 0.8512419999999999, 0.013111], [0.481439, 0.593214, 0.441869, 0.013111]